        pinId: 実際値
    - from:
        insId: assert-064
        pinId: 完了
      to:
        insId: __this
        pinId: 完了
    - from:
        insId: set-rain
        pinId: 完了
      to:
        insId: Delay-ovg789hz
        pinId: value
    - from:
        insId: Delay-ovg789hz
        pinId: delayedValue
      to:
        insId: get-weather-rain
        pinId: トリガー
    - from:
        insId: set-clear
        pinId: 完了
      to:
        insId: Delay-ls7qh5am
        pinId: value
    - from:
        insId: Delay-ls7qh5am
        pinId: delayedValue
      to:
        insId: get-weather-clear
        pinId: トリガー
  id: AutoCommand
  inputs:
    トリガー: required
  outputs:
    完了: {}
  inputsPosition:
    トリガー:
      x: -100
      y: 200
  outputsPosition:
    完了:
      x: 950
      y: 2300
  completionOutputs:
    - 完了
  description: |
    自動コマンドテスト（TC-051〜054/056〜064）トリガー入力で順番に自動実行
    TC-051: RunCommand(time set day) → Assert(完了=true)
    TC-052: RunCommand(time set 6000) → GetGameTime → Assert(時刻≈6000)
    TC-053: IsDaytime → Assert(昼=true)
    TC-054: GetWeather → Assert(天気 neq "")
    TC-056: RunCommand(weather rain) → GetWeather → Assert(天気=Rain)
    TC-057: RunCommand(weather clear) → GetWeather → Assert(天気=Clear)
    TC-058: RunCommand(gamemode creative) → GetGameMode → Assert(Creative)
    TC-059: RunCommand(gamemode survival) → GetGameMode → Assert(Survival)
    TC-060: GetTopSolidBlock → Vector3Split → Assert(y >= -64)
    TC-061: WorldQuery×3種別 → 例外なく完了することを確認（ログで確認）
    TC-064: RunCommand(setblock) → FillBlocks → Assert(個数 >= 0)
